text: Masala Thosai is crispy and well made, curry is nice too. Serving size is large, I almost cannot finish.

Annae, your biryani and curry is better than some joker at TEN MILE JUNCTION. but your minyak is send people to hospital for heart attack bypass surgery. I think cooking oil price go up because of you. The amount of oil you use is enough to send a spacecraft for a Mission to Mars and can return back with more than enough fuel left. Based on google ratings, looks like your shop will die quite soon. Buck up or balik kampung.

On 6th Sept 2024 at 1030 am, we ordered Egg with oninion Parata. My wife ordered appam. The worse parata not cooked well inside and hopless curry. The Appam was even worse. But Appam was returned and refunded the Appam money. Appam flour was incorrect and not cooked in the center. The owner need to relook at thier quality of food seriosly. Disappointed.
The combination of curry and coconut chutney with the egg and onion thosai tastes great. The portion is large and the price is very reasonable. Fast service and friendly staff .
Thosai is good, but better not to take anything else (especially the mutton: 6$ for one piece of rubber).
